A. Tips and tricks

1. Path

Yii::getAlias('@app')

@yii - framework directory.

@app - base path of currently running application. C:\xampp\htdocs\framework\backend/

@runtime - runtime directory.

@vendor - Composer vendor directory.

@webroot - web root directory of currently running web application. C:/xampp/htdocs/framework/backend/web

@web - base URL of currently running web application. /framework/backend/web

2. Pjax use
data-pjax = "0" not working on grid if format = 'html'
=> format => 'row'
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
disable pjax for link or button => data-pjax = "0"


3. PHPStorm settings

PHPStorm Update
Settings | Editor | Inspections | PHP | Error handling | Unhandled exception
=> Disable
Settings | Editor | Inspections | PHP | Composer | Extension is missing in composer.json
